file.content:
openapi: 3.0.2
info:
  title: Entities
  version: "1.0"
paths:
  /person:
    put:
      summary: Update an existing person
      description: Update an existing person by Id
      operationId: updatePerson
      requestBody:
        description: Update an existent person in the store
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: string
              default: abc
        required: false
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Successful operation
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: string
